Whitespace for text block indent should be consistent
Why is this an issue? Either use only spaces or only tabs for the indentation of a text block. Mixing white space will lead to a result with irregular indentation. 
### Noncompliant
String textBlock = """
        this is
<tab>text block!
        !!!!
      """;
 
### Compliant
String textBlock = """
        this is
        text block!
        !!!!
      """;
 Resources JEP 378: Text Blocks Programmerâ€™s Guide To Text Blocks, by Jim Laskey and Stuart Marks
